properties.title: Accrobranche du Dahu
properties.abstract: Obstacle course in the trees situated in Champery, the Accrobranche du Dahu will surprise you : zip lines, suspension bridges, lianas, climbing nets and other activities will be awaiting you.
properties.description:
In family, with friends, on a school trip or business outing, the Champéry Aventure Team Parc allows you to escape form everyday life and reach personal limits. Unforgettable moments full of emotion are guaranteed.

This park allows everyone to enjoy nature and experience different emotions. Easier courses for little ones or adapted courses for bigger ones, the park will live up to all of your expectations.

Finally, the highlight of the park is the « Tyro » course: 8 breathtaking zip lines lined up one after the other (one is 180m long).
properties.name: Champéry Aventure Team Parc
